Update References to Your Force.com Site URLs
Ensure continued access to your sites when the temporary redirection of legacy Salesforce domains ends, starting in September 2024 for production orgs. Update references to your old *.force.com site URLs.

Where: This change applies to Aura, LWR, and Visualforce sites accessed through Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Preparing for Legacy Salesforce Domain Changes
